A added bonus to this slick style is the pull tab which comes with a fuzzy blue piece inspired by the beloved Cookie Monster’s furry coat – complete with his eyes featured on the ankle collar! The performance of this shoe is achieved through the lightweight Flow midsole/outsole construction as well as Steph Curry's logo on the lateral side. Enjoy you adventures in style and maximum performance every time in your Under Armour Sesame Street x Curry Flow 9 GS 'Street Pack Cookie Monster' sneaker.
